The paper deals with a communication system (massive MIMO) and proposes a scheme to mitigate pilot contamination. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also deals with network interference and allocation of resources, which suggests categories such as cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also mentions simulations, which suggests categories such as cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
